<h5 id="bonus-post-tcr-summary-statistics">Bonus post: TCR summary statistics</h5>

<p>In part 1, I showed that a simple approach allows for specific detection of TCR transcripts in mature thymocytes. In part 2, I gave the exact details of the method. The important work is done, at least as befits our lab‚Äôs priorities for that project, and this post is purely for amusement.</p>

<p>As long as I had all the human TCR segments in a tidy dataframe, I decided to display some basic properties. Here‚Äôs the length and number of known segments by type and by locus.</p>

